 Megadeth 自 2006 年以来首次表演稀有曲目“Liar” https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-perform-rarity-liar-for-first-time-since-2006-3783149?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=megadeth-perform-rarity-liar-for- 2006 年以来首次Surej SinghTue, 13 Aug 2024 05:58:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetal https://www.nme.com/?p=3783149 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="美国鞭打金属乐队 Megadeth 的 Dave Mustaine 在音乐会上表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “到目前为止，一切都很好……那又怎样！”自 2000 年代以来，这首歌只播放了 10 次</p><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-perform-rarity-liar-for-first-time-since-2006-3783149">Megadeth 表演自 2006 年以来的稀有曲目“Liar”首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="美国鞭打金属乐队 Megadeth 的 Dave Mustaine 在音乐会上表演" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/megadeth-dave-mustaine@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megadeth">Megadeth</a>自 2006 年以来首次现场表演“Liar”——观看下面的表演片段。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/speed-only-one-mode-album-review-radar-3774863">速度——“只有一种模式”评论：不妥协且不可否认</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周五（8 月 9 日），在加利福尼亚州英格尔伍德演出时，传奇的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-mustaine">Dave Mustaine</a>领衔的鞭打金属乐队爆发了“So Far, So Good...So What!”歌曲18年来首次现场直播。</p><p>这首歌摘自他们 1988 年的第三张录音室专辑，是乐队曲目中表演最少的歌曲之一——它在 2000 年代只现场演奏了 10 次，在 1990 年代演奏了 27 次，在 1980 年代演奏了 36 次。</p><p>在开始这首歌之前，马斯泰恩问加州的人群：“我有一个问题要问你们——今晚我有一个问题要问大家。你希望我们演奏一首我们已经演奏了大约 20 年的歌曲吗？”</p><p>请观看下面 Megadeth 表演的“Liar”。 </p><p><iframe title="Megadeth LIAR Live 2024 年洛杉矶 YouTube 剧院 20 年来首次" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2ovTNDUY2aw?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>六月，乐队最新的贝斯手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-actively-recording-new-album-with-david-ellefsons-replacement-3768985">James LoMenzo 透露，Megadeth 正在“积极”创作新音乐</a>。此前，乐队因长期贝斯手大卫·埃勒夫森 (David Ellefson) 受到指控而与他分手。</p><p> 2021 年，社交媒体上发布了几张露骨的截图和视频后，针对这位前 Megadeth 贝斯手的指控浮出水面。当时，埃勒夫森说他们是“私人和私人谈话”——但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeths-david-ellefson-denies-grooming-allegations-2937314">据称他已经诱骗了一名未成年女孩</a>。</p><p> Megadeth 宣布他们当年与这位贝斯手分道扬镳，在此期间他否认有任何不当行为，并对<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-megadeth-bassist-david-ellefson-admits-to-masturbating-encounters-with-woman-in-new-police-report-2963812" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-megadeth-bassist-david-ellefson-admits-to-masturbating-encounters-with-woman-in-new-police-report-2963812&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1658089900707000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1hRRSPkwZupNlo2iOpIPyB">他声称非法泄露视频和屏幕截图的人提出报复性色情指控</a>，从而引发了对他的指控。埃勒夫森坚称，涉事女子当时并非未成年。</p><p>去年，艾勒夫森在穆斯坦被乐队解雇后对他进行了猛烈抨击，称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-ellefson-says-its-fucking-pathetic-that-dave-mustaine-is-still-bitching-about-getting-kicked-out-of-metallica-3443394">他“还在抱怨”被踢出金属乐队，这“太可悲了”</a> 。在艾勒夫森受到指控后，穆斯坦出面表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeths-dave-mustaine-says-hell-forgive-david-ellefson-but-just-wont-play-music-with-him-anymore-3257121">他会“原谅”他，但“只是不再和他一起演奏音乐”</a> 。</p><p>继<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-perform-rarity-liar-for-first-time-since-2006-3783149">Megadeth 表演自 2006 年以来的稀有曲目“Liar”首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
